      "localizations": {
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ассистент печатает"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "At least %lld characters. Gemocode can't recover a forgotten passphrase.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Не менее %lld символов. Gemocode не сможет восстановить забытую кодовую фразу."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Attach photos or PDFs to your reports and they'll all appear here.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
